{"id":67869,"title":"Putting the 'C' back into continuous renal replacement therapy.","abstract":"It may seem obvious that continuous renal replacement therapy (CRRT) means that the treatment is truly continuous--administered without interruption on a 24/7 basis. In reality, a number of barriers limit the continuous aspect of CRRT. This article describes how nursing staff of an inpatient dialysis unit in a large Midwestern academic institution identified these barriers and developed and implemented a multifaceted plan to optimize CRRT.","date":"2014-03-03","categories":"Male Urogenital Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24579397","annotations":[{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.750806,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Kidney","weight":0.709922,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kidney"},{"name":"Dialysis","weight":0.625776,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dialysis"},{"name":"Nursing","weight":0.471201,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nursing"},{"name":"Inpatient","weight":0.464908,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inpatient"},{"name":"Nurse","weight":0.359522,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nurse"},{"name":"Midwestern United States","weight":0.219076,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Midwestern_United_States"},{"name":"Hemofiltration","weight":0.162776,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hemofiltration"},{"name":"Institution","weight":0.0805305,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Institution"},{"name":"Academia","weight":0.0805305,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Academia"},{"name":"Continuous and progressive aspects","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Continuous_and_progressive_aspects"},{"name":"Renal replacement therapy","weight":0.0287296,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Renal_replacement_therapy"},{"name":"Reality","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reality"},{"name":"Continuous function","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Continuous_function"},{"name":"Grammatical aspect","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grammatical_aspect"},{"name":"247","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/247"},{"name":"Academic institution","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Academic_institution"},{"name":"Celsius","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Celsius"},{"name":"Operations research","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Operations_research"},{"name":"Military organization","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Military_organization"}]}
